{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 300°F, line a baking sheet with parchment and set aside. Place a large bowl onto mixing bowl lid, weigh in popcorn and set aside."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place egg white, honey and salt into mixing bowl and without measuring cup whisk <nobr>30 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>.","Add almonds, pecans, cashews, Mexican spice, sesame seeds and cayenne and without measuring cup cook <nobr>5 min\/250°F\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. Add butter, insert measuring cup and cook a further <nobr>30 sec\/250°F\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Transfer nut mixture to large bowl with reserved popcorn and toss with spatula to combine. Transfer onto prepared baking sheet and bake for 20 minutes (300°F) stirring after 10 minutes to ensure even baking. Do not overbake. Allow to cool before transferring to serving bowls."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["2 oz popcorn (popped), buttered and salted","1 egg white, from a large egg","1 oz honey","¼ tsp salt, to taste","4 oz raw almonds, skin on","4 oz raw pecans","4 oz cashews","1 - 2 tbsp Mexican spice mix, to taste","2 tbsp sesame seeds              (optional)","½ tsp cayenne pepper, to taste","1 oz unsalted butter, diced (½ in.)"]}],"id":"r294955","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-wr6t1Ad5ne8\/XZapfmJqwaI\/AAAAAAAAhRQ\/5lt5PS4KihoepIH8p3EbM048DBZsna9SACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_0--A1Y_u2uu_X-A9.png","title":"Spicy Nuts and Popcorn Party Mix","publishedAt":"2018-01-12T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"40 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"23 g","calories":"1946 kJ \/ 465 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking sheet, parchment paper, large bowl, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","6 portions"]}